    <article class="markdown-body entry-content container-lg f5" itemprop="text"><div class="markdown-heading" dir="auto"><h1 class="heading-element" dir="auto">💫 About Me:</h1><a id="user-content--about-me" class="anchor" aria-label="Permalink: 💫 About Me:" href="#-about-me"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"></path></svg></a></div>
<p dir="auto"><br><br>With over 10 years of experience in software development and team leadership, I specialize in building scalable web and mobile applications using technologies like React JS, Redux, RTK Query, React Native, Vue JS, Angular, NgRx, Node JS, and more. I’ve also worked extensively with back-end stacks such as Python, SQLAlchemy, Alembic, C#, .NET Core, and cloud platforms including AWS, GCP, and Azure.<br><br>In recent years, I’ve focused on AI-powered development, integrating OpenAI, Anthropic, and other LLM APIs into production systems. I’ve built conversational assistants, document summarization tools, and AI-driven dashboards that automate workflows and improve decision-making. My work often involves practical prompt engineering, RAG pipelines, and chat-based UX that bring LLM capabilities directly into user-facing products.<br><br>I also have hands-on experience in Blockchain development, having built analytical bots, automated trading systems, and custom token contracts on the Ethereum network — blending Web3 automation with data-driven logic.<br><br>My DevOps background includes setting up CI/CD pipelines with GitHub Actions, Jenkins, and Azure DevOps, and configuring observability with Datadog and Sentry to ensure reliability and performance.<br><br>Beyond technical expertise, I lead and mentor cross-functional teams in agile environments, ensuring alignment between business goals and engineering output. I value clear communication, ownership, and iterative improvement as the foundation of high-performing teams.<br><br>I’m passionate about combining AI, automation, and scalable architecture to build products that make complex systems smarter, faster, and more human-friendly.</p>
<div class="markdown-heading" dir="auto"><h2 class="heading-element" dir="auto">🌐 Socials:</h2><a id="user-content--socials" class="anchor" aria-label="Permalink: 🌐 Socials:" href="#-socials"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"></path></svg></a></div>
